        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2017-08-14T18:01:55Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Recognizes the dangers of distracted driving.</p> <p> Expresses support for:</p> <ul> <li>efforts to educate the public about such dangers;</li> <li>AT&amp;T's &quot;It Can Wait&quot; campaign to raise awareness of such dangers;</li> <li>industry-led engineering solutions to reduce fatal crash risks as a result of distracted driving;</li> <li>stronger enforcement of distracted driving laws; and </li> <li>the Road to Zero coalition and its efforts to encourage a holistic, safe system approach to improving roadway safety.</li> </ul>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
